{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":508,"text":"In the ocean,"},{"time":1540,"text":"what is the common point"},{"time":3380,"text":"between oil, plastic and radioactivity?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":9148,"text":"On the top line, this is the BP oil spill:"},{"time":14365,"text":"billions of barrels of oil gushing"},{"time":16388,"text":"in the Gulf of Mexico."},{"time":17757,"text":"The middle line is millions of tons of"},{"time":19932,"text":"plastic debris accumulating in our ocean,"},{"time":22336,"text":"and the third line is radioactive material"},{"time":25056,"text":"leaking from Fukushima nuclear power plant"},{"time":27352,"text":"in the Pacific Ocean."}]},{"cues":[{"time":28690,"text":"Well, the three big problems have in common"},{"time":33273,"text":"that they are man-made problems"},{"time":36088,"text":"but they are controlled by natural forces."},{"time":38144,"text":"This should make us feel very, terribly awful"},{"time":42552,"text":"as much as it should make us feel hopeful,"},{"time":44879,"text":"because if we have the power to create these problems,"},{"time":47688,"text":"we may as well have the power"},{"time":49368,"text":"to remediate these problems."}]},{"cues":[{"time":50800,"text":"But what about natural forces?"},{"time":52744,"text":"Well, that's exactly what I want to talk about today,"},{"time":55727,"text":"is how we can use these natural forces"},{"time":58032,"text":"to remediate these man-made problems."},{"time":63255,"text":"When the BP oil spill happened,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":64481,"text":"I was working at MIT, and I was in charge"},{"time":67246,"text":"of developing an oil spill-cleaning technology."},{"time":69643,"text":"And I had a chance to go in the Gulf of Mexico"},{"time":73056,"text":"and meet some fishermen and see"},{"time":75393,"text":"the terrible conditions in which they were working."},{"time":77184,"text":"More than 700 of these boats,"},{"time":80265,"text":"which are fishermen boats repurposed"},{"time":82572,"text":"with oil absorbent in white"},{"time":85033,"text":"and oil containment in orange, were used,"},{"time":87428,"text":"but they only collected three percent of the oil on the surface,"},{"time":90687,"text":"and the health of the cleaners"},{"time":92399,"text":"were very deeply affected."}]},{"cues":[{"time":94312,"text":"I was working on a very interesting technology"},{"time":98306,"text":"at MIT, but it was a very long-term view"},{"time":100615,"text":"of how to develop technology,"},{"time":102049,"text":"and it was going to be a very expensive technology,"},{"time":104567,"text":"and also it would be patented."},{"time":107015,"text":"So I wanted to develop something that we could"},{"time":109647,"text":"develop very fast, that would be cheap,"},{"time":113047,"text":"and that would be open-source, so, because"},{"time":115487,"text":"oil spills are not only happening in the Gulf of Mexico,"},{"time":117655,"text":"and that would be using renewable energy."},{"time":120271,"text":"So I quit my dream job,"},{"time":122671,"text":"and I moved to New Orleans,"},{"time":124287,"text":"and I kept on studying how the oil spill was happening."}]},{"cues":[{"time":127231,"text":"Currently, what they were doing is"},{"time":129303,"text":"that they were using these small fishing boats,"},{"time":130949,"text":"and they were cleaning clean lines in an ocean of dirt."},{"time":134109,"text":"If you're using the exact same amount of surface"},{"time":137822,"text":"of oil absorbent, but you're just paying attention"},{"time":139975,"text":"to natural patterns, and if you're going up the winds,"},{"time":142308,"text":"you can collect a lot more material."},{"time":144076,"text":"If you're multiplying the rig,"},{"time":146197,"text":"so you multiply how many layers of absorbent"},{"time":148772,"text":"you're using, you can collect a lot more."},{"time":150674,"text":"But it's extremely difficult to move oil absorbent"},{"time":153275,"text":"against the winds, the surface currents and the waves."},{"time":156907,"text":"These are enormous forces."},{"time":158371,"text":"So the very simple idea was to use the ancient technique"},{"time":161394,"text":"of sailing and tacking of the wind"},{"time":163647,"text":"to capture or intercept the oil"},{"time":166265,"text":"that is drifting down the wind."},{"time":167607,"text":"So this didn't require any invention."},{"time":171104,"text":"We just took a simple sailing boat"},{"time":172807,"text":"and we tried to pull something long and heavy,"},{"time":174704,"text":"but as we tacked back and forth,"},{"time":177016,"text":"what we lost was two things:"},{"time":178687,"text":"we were losing pulling power and direction."}]},{"cues":[{"time":182064,"text":"And so, I thought, what about if we just take the rudder"},{"time":185896,"text":"from the back of the boat to the front,"},{"time":187408,"text":"would we have better control?"},{"time":189151,"text":"So I built this small sailing robot"},{"time":191367,"text":"with the rudder at the front,"},{"time":192615,"text":"and I was trying to pull something very long and heavy,"},{"time":195080,"text":"so that's a four-meter-long object just to pull,"},{"time":198287,"text":"and I was surprised with just a 14-centimeter rudder,"},{"time":201199,"text":"I could control four meters of absorbent."},{"time":203551,"text":"Then I was so happy that I kept playing with the robot,"},{"time":207367,"text":"and so you see the robot has"},{"time":209831,"text":"a front rudder here."},{"time":211503,"text":"Normally it's at the back."},{"time":212719,"text":"And, playing, I realized that the maneuverability"},{"time":216334,"text":"of this was really amazing,"},{"time":217614,"text":"and I could avoid an obstacle at the very last second,"},{"time":219542,"text":"more maneuverable than a normal boat."}]},{"cues":[{"time":221214,"text":"Then I started publishing online, and"},{"time":224078,"text":"some friends from Korea, they started being"},{"time":226990,"text":"interested in this, and we made a boat"},{"time":228719,"text":"which has a front rudder and a back rudder,"},{"time":230527,"text":"so we started interacting with this,"},{"time":232585,"text":"and it was slightly better,"},{"time":234704,"text":"although it was very small and a bit off balance,"},{"time":236628,"text":"but then we thought,"},{"time":237708,"text":"what if we have more than two points of control?"},{"time":239596,"text":"What if the entire boat becomes a point of control?"},{"time":241588,"text":"What if the entire boat changes shape?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":243708,"text":"So â€” (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":246148,"text":"Thank you very much. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":248044,"text":"And so that's the beginning of Protei,"},{"time":250629,"text":"and that's the first boat in history"},{"time":252268,"text":"that completely changed the shape of the hull"},{"time":253892,"text":"in order to control it,"},{"time":255062,"text":"and the properties of sailing that we get"},{"time":257948,"text":"are very superior compared to a normal boat."},{"time":260846,"text":"When we're turning, we have the feeling of surfing,"},{"time":263500,"text":"and the way it's going up-wind, it's very efficient."},{"time":267616,"text":"This is low speed, low wind speed,"},{"time":270316,"text":"and the maneuverability is very increased,"},{"time":272389,"text":"and here I'm going to do a small jibe,"},{"time":274700,"text":"and look at the position of the sail."},{"time":276796,"text":"What's happening is that, because the boat changes shape,"},{"time":280396,"text":"the position of the front sail and the main sail"},{"time":282736,"text":"are different to the wind."},{"time":283913,"text":"We're catching wind from both sides."},{"time":285796,"text":"And this is exactly what we're looking [for]"},{"time":288055,"text":"if we want to pull something long and heavy."},{"time":289839,"text":"We don't want to lose pulling power, nor direction."},{"time":292228,"text":"So, I wanted to know if this was possible"},{"time":295068,"text":"to put this at an industrial level,"},{"time":296539,"text":"so we made a large boat with a large sail,"},{"time":299051,"text":"and with a very light hull, inflatable,"},{"time":301747,"text":"very small footprint,"},{"time":303252,"text":"so we have a very big size and power ratio."}]},{"cues":[{"time":306076,"text":"After this, we wanted to see if we could"},{"time":309307,"text":"implement this and automate the system,"},{"time":311604,"text":"so we used the same system but we added"},{"time":313276,"text":"a structure to it so we could activate the machine."},{"time":315646,"text":"So, we used the same bladder-inflated system,"},{"time":318860,"text":"and we took it for testing."},{"time":320844,"text":"So this is happening in the Netherlands."},{"time":323155,"text":"We tried in the water without any skin or ballast"},{"time":325686,"text":"just to see how it works."},{"time":328257,"text":"And then we mounted a camera for controlling it,"},{"time":330942,"text":"but quickly we saw that we would need"},{"time":333844,"text":"a lot more weight at the bottom,"},{"time":335993,"text":"so we had to take it back to the lab,"},{"time":337530,"text":"and then we built a skin around it,"},{"time":339618,"text":"we put batteries, remote controllers, and then"},{"time":342905,"text":"we put it in the water and then we"},{"time":344353,"text":"let it go in the water and see how well it would work,"},{"time":347514,"text":"so let some rope out, and hope it's going to work,"},{"time":350938,"text":"and it worked okay, but we still have a long way."},{"time":354161,"text":"Our small prototype has given us good insight"},{"time":356597,"text":"that it's working very well,"},{"time":357943,"text":"but we still need to work a lot more on this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":360628,"text":"So what we are doing is an accelerated evolution"},{"time":364497,"text":"of sailing technology."},{"time":365945,"text":"We went from a back rudder to a front rudder"},{"time":367872,"text":"to two rudders to multiple rudders"},{"time":369883,"text":"to the whole boat changing shape,"},{"time":371554,"text":"and the more we are moving forward,"},{"time":373410,"text":"and the more the design looks simple and cute. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":379457,"text":"But I wanted to show you a fish because --"},{"time":381834,"text":"In fact, it's very different from a fish."},{"time":384904,"text":"A fish will move because -- by changing like this,"},{"time":389304,"text":"but our boat is propelled by the wind still,"},{"time":392403,"text":"and the hull controls the trajectory."}]},{"cues":[{"time":394810,"text":"So I brought to you for the first time on the TED stage"},{"time":398464,"text":"Protei Number Eight. It's not the last one,"},{"time":400849,"text":"but it's a good one for making demos."}]},{"cues":[{"time":403098,"text":"So the first thing as I show you in the video is"},{"time":405374,"text":"that we may be able to control the trajectory"},{"time":409361,"text":"of a sailing boat better,"},{"time":410825,"text":"or we may be able to never be in irons,"},{"time":413886,"text":"so never facing the wind,"},{"time":415186,"text":"we always can catch the wind from both sides."},{"time":417301,"text":"But new properties of a sailing boat."},{"time":419861,"text":"So if you're looking at the boat from this side,"},{"time":424117,"text":"this might remind you of an airplane profile."},{"time":426325,"text":"An airplane, when you're moving in this direction,"},{"time":428738,"text":"starts to lift, and that's how it takes off."},{"time":431003,"text":"Now, if you're taking the same system,"},{"time":433178,"text":"and you're putting vertical, you're bending,"},{"time":435546,"text":"and if you're moving this way forward,"},{"time":437546,"text":"your instinct will tell you that you might go this way,"},{"time":440673,"text":"but if you're moving fast enough,"},{"time":442480,"text":"you might create what we call lateral lift,"},{"time":444499,"text":"so we could get further or closer to the wind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":447424,"text":"Other property is this:"},{"time":450368,"text":"A normal sailing boat has a centerboard here"},{"time":453529,"text":"and a rudder at the back,"},{"time":455521,"text":"and these two things are what creates most"},{"time":458071,"text":"resistance and turbulence behind the boat,"},{"time":460725,"text":"but because this doesn't have either"},{"time":462996,"text":"a centerboard or a rudder,"},{"time":464532,"text":"we hope that if we keep working on this hull design"},{"time":467404,"text":"we can improve and have less resistance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":469596,"text":"The other thing is, most boats, when they reach"},{"time":472251,"text":"a certain speed, and they are going on waves,"},{"time":474475,"text":"they start to hit and slap on the surface of the water,"},{"time":476914,"text":"and a lot of the energy moving forward is lost."},{"time":480211,"text":"But if we're going with the flow,"},{"time":482299,"text":"if we pay attention to natural patterns"},{"time":484435,"text":"instead of trying to be strong,"},{"time":486046,"text":"but if you're going with the flow, we may absorb"},{"time":488445,"text":"a lot of environmental noises, so the wave energy,"},{"time":491642,"text":"to actually save some energy to move forward."}]},{"cues":[{"time":494799,"text":"So we may have developed the technology"},{"time":498950,"text":"which is very efficient for pulling something long and heavy,"},{"time":501617,"text":"but the idea is, what is the purpose of technology"},{"time":505834,"text":"if it doesn't reach the right hands?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":507780,"text":"Normal technology or innovation happens like this:"},{"time":510726,"text":"Somebody has an interesting idea,"},{"time":513156,"text":"some other scientist or engineer,"},{"time":515118,"text":"they take it to the next level, they make a theory about it"},{"time":517622,"text":"and maybe they patent it,"},{"time":518878,"text":"and then some industry will make a contract"},{"time":521414,"text":"of exclusivity to manufacture and sell it,"},{"time":524558,"text":"and then, eventually, a buyer will buy it,"},{"time":526654,"text":"and we hope that they are going to use [it] for a good purpose."},{"time":529422,"text":"What we really want is that this innovation happens"},{"time":533118,"text":"continuously. The inventor and engineers"},{"time":535454,"text":"and also the manufacturers and everybody"},{"time":537190,"text":"works at the same time, but this would be sterile"},{"time":539574,"text":"if this was happening in a parallel and uncrossed process."},{"time":543206,"text":"What you really want is not a sequential,"},{"time":545246,"text":"not parallel development."},{"time":546638,"text":"You want to have a network of innovation."},{"time":548247,"text":"You want everybody, like we're doing now,"},{"time":550326,"text":"to work at the same time, and that can only happen"},{"time":553495,"text":"if these people all together decide to share the information,"},{"time":556886,"text":"and that's exactly what open hardware is about."},{"time":559826,"text":"It's to replace competition by collaboration."},{"time":563495,"text":"It's to transform any new product into a new market."},{"time":567646,"text":"So what is open hardware?"},{"time":570087,"text":"Essentially, open hardware is a license."},{"time":571870,"text":"It's just an intellectual property setup."},{"time":573942,"text":"It means that everybody is free to use,"},{"time":576966,"text":"modify and distribute, and in exchange"},{"time":580119,"text":"we only ask for two things:"},{"time":581397,"text":"The name is credited -- the name of the project --"},{"time":583492,"text":"and also the people who make improvement,"},{"time":586228,"text":"they share back with the community."},{"time":587556,"text":"So it's a very simple condition."}]},{"cues":[{"time":588892,"text":"And I started this project alone in a garage in New Orleans,"},{"time":592916,"text":"but quickly after I wanted to publish and share"},{"time":595092,"text":"this information, so I made a Kickstarter,"},{"time":596836,"text":"which is a crowd-fundraising platform,"},{"time":599076,"text":"and in about one month we fundraised 30,000 dollars."},{"time":601508,"text":"With this money, I hired a team of young engineers"},{"time":604820,"text":"from all over the world, and we rented a factory"},{"time":607348,"text":"in Rotterdam in the Netherlands."},{"time":608868,"text":"We were peer-learning, we were engineering,"},{"time":612029,"text":"we were making things, prototyping,"},{"time":615212,"text":"but most importantly we were trying our prototypes"},{"time":617437,"text":"in the water as often as possible,"},{"time":619132,"text":"to fail as quickly as possible, to learn from."},{"time":622284,"text":"This is a proud member of Protei from Korea,"},{"time":624796,"text":"and on the right side, this is a multiple-masts"},{"time":627256,"text":"design proposed by a team in Mexico."},{"time":629189,"text":"This idea really appealed to Gabriella Levine"},{"time":632374,"text":"in New York, and so she decided to prototype"},{"time":634969,"text":"this idea that she saw, and she documented"},{"time":637499,"text":"every step of the process,"},{"time":638928,"text":"and she published it on Instructables,"},{"time":641177,"text":"which is a website for sharing inventions."},{"time":643409,"text":"Less than one week after,"},{"time":645304,"text":"this is a team in Eindhoven, it's a school of engineering."},{"time":649314,"text":"They made it, but they eventually published"},{"time":651644,"text":"a simplified design."},{"time":652768,"text":"They also made it into an Instructable,"},{"time":654697,"text":"and in less than one week, they had"},{"time":656432,"text":"almost 10,000 views, and they got many new friends."},{"time":659192,"text":"We're working on also simpler technology,"},{"time":662096,"text":"not that complex, with younger people"},{"time":664047,"text":"and also older people,"},{"time":665616,"text":"like this dinosaur is from Mexico. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":668767,"text":"So Protei is now an international network"},{"time":671584,"text":"of innovation for selling technology"},{"time":674432,"text":"using this shape-shifting hull."},{"time":676224,"text":"And what puts us together is that we have a common,"},{"time":680259,"text":"at least, global understanding"},{"time":683048,"text":"of what the word \"business\" is, or what it should be."},{"time":686120,"text":"This is how most work today."},{"time":688353,"text":"Business as usual is saying, what's most important"},{"time":690727,"text":"is to make lots of profit, and you'll be using"},{"time":692966,"text":"technology for that, and people will be your work force,"},{"time":695791,"text":"instrumentalized,"},{"time":697039,"text":"and environment is usually the last priority."},{"time":699711,"text":"It will be just a way to, say, greenwash your audience"},{"time":703589,"text":"and, say, increase your price tag."}]},{"cues":[{"time":705820,"text":"What we're trying to do, or what we believe,"},{"time":708349,"text":"because this is how we believe the world really works,"},{"time":710765,"text":"is that without the environment you have nothing."},{"time":712935,"text":"We have the people so we need to protect each other, yes,"},{"time":715820,"text":"and we're a technology company,"},{"time":717484,"text":"and profit is necessary to make this happen. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":722669,"text":"Thank you very much. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":726274,"text":"If we have the courage to understand or accept"},{"time":730355,"text":"that this actually how the world really works,"},{"time":732275,"text":"and this is the order of priority that we need to choose,"},{"time":735292,"text":"then it makes obvious why we need"},{"time":737433,"text":"to choose open hardware for developing environmental"},{"time":739772,"text":"technology, because we need to share information."}]},{"cues":[{"time":741652,"text":"What's next for us?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":743732,"text":"So, this small machine that you've seen,"},{"time":746267,"text":"we're hoping to make small toys like"},{"time":748411,"text":"one-meter remote control Protei that you can upgrade --"},{"time":751904,"text":"so replace the remote control parts by Androids,"},{"time":754890,"text":"so the mobile phone, and Arduino micro-controller,"},{"time":758669,"text":"so you could be controlling this"},{"time":759892,"text":"from your mobile phone, your tablet."},{"time":761380,"text":"Then what we want to do is create six-meter versions"},{"time":764946,"text":"so we can test the maximum performance of these machines,"},{"time":767274,"text":"so we can go at very, very high speed."},{"time":768838,"text":"So imagine yourself."},{"time":770101,"text":"You are laying down in a flexible torpedo,"},{"time":773286,"text":"sailing at high speed,"},{"time":774780,"text":"controlling the shape of the hull with your legs"},{"time":776625,"text":"and controlling the sail with your arms."},{"time":779287,"text":"So that's what we're looking for developing. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":783612,"text":"And we replace the human being --"},{"time":785826,"text":"to go, for example, for measuring radioactivity,"},{"time":787970,"text":"you don't want a human to be sailing those robots --"},{"time":790149,"text":"with batteries, motors, micro-controllers and sensors."},{"time":793484,"text":"This is what our teammates, we dream of at night."},{"time":797418,"text":"We hope that we can sometime clean up oil spills,"},{"time":800070,"text":"or we can gather or collect plastic in the ocean,"},{"time":804047,"text":"or we can have swarms of our machines"},{"time":807481,"text":"controlled by multi-player video game engines"},{"time":810663,"text":"to control many of these machines,"},{"time":812614,"text":"to monitor coral reefs"},{"time":814365,"text":"or to monitor fisheries."}]},{"cues":[{"time":816504,"text":"Our hope is that we can use open hardware technology"},{"time":820994,"text":"to better understand and protect our oceans."}]},{"cues":[{"time":824525,"text":"Thank you very much. (Applause)"},{"time":828237,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}